iaik.pkcs.pkcs11.parameters

Interface DHKeyDerivationParameters.KeyDerivationFunctionType

  • Enclosing class:
    DHKeyDerivationParameters

    public static interface DHKeyDerivationParameters.KeyDerivationFunctionType
    This interface defines the available key derivation function types as defined by PKCS#11: CKD_NULL, CKD_SHA1_KDF, CKD_SHA1_KDF_ASN1, CKD_SHA1_KDF_CONCATENATE.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Karl Scheibelhofer
